null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261478}, {"id": 21522, "content": "有wifi有wifi有wifi", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278294}, {"id": 20755, "content": "一台XBOX ONE！微软大法好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207262}, {"id": 21523, "content": "重点是它能像港湾一样，不管一个人还是两个人，只有愿意住，住的舒心才是家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267513}, {"id": 20756, "content": "落地窗大床有一个类似于外国车库一样的空间外面有树没噪音有点像曲径通幽处的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272575}, {"id": 21012, "content": "有你，有我，还有我们的Ta", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211509yXlfJFbht56ArmcM.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274679}, {"id": 20759, "content": "首先是人，然后是书、游戏、美酒、佳肴", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 194834}, {"id": 20765, "content": "得有大阳台", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272595}, {"id": 20770, "content": "一只猫和一个女人还有堆书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272624}, {"id": 20771, "content": "必须有家人在，不然再怎么舒适只是一栋房子罢了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257588}, {"id": 21795, "content": "满冰箱的酸奶饮料吃不完的零食体感游戏机软的把我包起来的床垫超快网速以及一个我一见就会笑的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281700}, {"id": 20772, "content": "狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259448}, {"id": 20773, "content": "女票", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272649}, {"id": 20776, "content": "wifi 大床 一群女人。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215666}, {"id": 20779, "content": "沙发，电视，两个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272296}, {"id": 20780, "content": "进门知道鞋架在哪，大衣能往哪挂。从客厅到厕所的距离要短，不然就会错过电视。厨房的香味从客厅刚好能闻到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272682}, {"id": 20781, "content": "舒适的沙发，可以横着竖着看电视", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216331}, {"id": 20782, "content": "简单一句 各种高科技 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 197771}, {"id": 20783, "content": "庭院?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230355}, {"id": 21039, "content": "有理解和欣赏！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274893}, {"id": 21296, "content": "我想有个家，家里有个她（他），白天么么哒，晚上啪啪哒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255265}, {"id": 20785, "content": "爱你的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252747}, {"id": 23348, "content": "好看舒适的床。冬暖夏凉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291856}, {"id": 20790, "content": "让自己安心的人 舒适干净的的床 高速的网 可口的饭菜和装满的冰箱还有零食柜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 268239}, {"id": 20792, "content": "有你，有我，我和我们共同的他（她）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183969}, {"id": 20794, "content": "有你，有我，和我们共同的他（ 她）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183969}, {"id": 20795, "content": "有你，有我，和我们共同的他（ 她）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183969}, {"id": 21307, "content": "没有房贷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243106}, {"id": 21563, "content": "哥哥哥哥哥哥哥哥根据成都市尽快恢复到手", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279120}, {"id": 23355, "content": "明亮的光线，暖暖的温度，干净的地板，软软的床，洁白柔软的床罩，宽带，咖啡，好耳机，好音乐。灿烂的阳光", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291882}, {"id": 21056, "content": "一个自己的世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274965}, {"id": 21568, "content": "得有爱人", "image": null, "praise_count":